## 12. Repository Structure

> **Note:** Updated to include OpenSearch + Fluent Bit in the stack.

**Decision:** Monorepo with a shared library (`kubex-common`). Every service and every agent depends on the shared library for schema contracts, auth primitives, and audit log format.

**Rationale:**
- The Structured Action Request schema, audit log format, and auth primitives are shared across every component. If these drift between components, the system breaks.
- A monorepo keeps the shared contract in one place тАФ change once, all components pick it up.
- Single `docker-compose.yml` at root for full-stack local dev.
- Each service/agent has its own Dockerfile and can build/deploy independently.
- Adding a new agent is just adding a folder тАФ no touching infrastructure code.

### Layout

```
openclaw/
тФЬтФАтФА BRAINSTORM.md
тФЬтФАтФА CLAUDE.md
тФЬтФАтФА docker-compose.yml              # Full stack local dev
тФЬтФАтФА docker-compose.dev.yml          # Dev overrides (hot reload, debug ports)
тФВ
тФЬтФАтФА libs/                            # Shared Python packages
тФВ   тФФтФАтФА kubex-common/                # THE shared contract library
тФВ       тФЬтФАтФА pyproject.toml
тФВ       тФФтФАтФА src/kubex_common/
тФВ           тФЬтФАтФА schemas/             # All data contracts
тФВ           тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА action_request.py    # Canonical ActionRequest (Section 16.2)
тФВ           тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА action_response.py   # Standard response envelope
тФВ           тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА agent_capability.py  # Capability advertisement schema
тФВ           тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА skill_manifest.py    # Skill definition schema (Section 16.1)
тФВ           тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА gatekeeper_envelope.py # GatekeeperEnvelope (Section 16.2)
тФВ           тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА routing.py           # RoutedRequest, BrokeredRequest, TaskDelivery (Section 16.3)
тФВ           тФВ   тФФтФАтФА actions/             # Per-action typed parameter schemas (Section 16.2)
тФВ           тФВ       тФЬтФАтФА __init__.py
тФВ           тФВ       тФЬтФАтФА http.py          # http_get, http_post, http_put params
тФВ           тФВ       тФЬтФАтФА email.py         # send_email params
тФВ           тФВ       тФЬтФАтФА storage.py       # write_output, read_input params
тФВ           тФВ       тФЬтФАтФА code.py          # execute_code params
тФВ           тФВ       тФЬтФАтФА dispatch.py      # dispatch_task params
тФВ           тФВ       тФЬтФАтФА lifecycle.py     # activate_kubex params
тФВ           тФВ       тФЬтФАтФА registry.py      # query_registry params
тФВ           тФВ       тФФтФАтФА result.py        # report_result params
тФВ           тФЬтФАтФА actions.py           # Global action vocabulary enum (ActionType)
тФВ           тФЬтФАтФА enums.py             # Tiers, decisions, agent status
тФВ           тФЬтФАтФА auth/                # Container identity verification
тФВ           тФЬтФАтФА audit/               # Audit log writer (shared format)
тФВ           тФЬтФАтФА config.py            # Shared config patterns
тФВ           тФЬтФАтФА skills/              # Built-in skills (referenced by kubex config.yaml)
тФВ           тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА __init__.py
тФВ           тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА model_selector.py    # Auto-select model from allowlist (Section 1)
тФВ           тФВ   тФФтФАтФА knowledge.py         # recall + memorize tools for knowledge base (Section 27.15)
тФВ           тФЬтФАтФА logging/             # Structured logging (Section 9)
тФВ           тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА __init__.py
тФВ           тФВ   тФФтФАтФА formatter.py     # Shared JSON log schema
тФВ           тФФтФАтФА metrics/             # Observability (Section 9)
тФВ               тФЬтФАтФА __init__.py
тФВ               тФФтФАтФА prometheus.py    # /metrics endpoint exporter
тФВ
тФЬтФАтФА services/                        # Infrastructure services (NOT agents)
тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА gateway/                     # Unified Gateway тАФ Policy Engine + Egress Proxy + Scheduler + Inbound Gate
тФВ   тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА Dockerfile
тФВ   тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА pyproject.toml           # depends on kubex-common
тФВ   тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА policies/               # YAML rule files
тФВ   тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА src/gateway/
тФВ   тФВ   тФФтФАтФА tests/
тФВ   тФВ
тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА kubex-manager/               # Docker lifecycle (create/start/stop/kill)
тФВ   тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА Dockerfile
тФВ   тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА pyproject.toml
тФВ   тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА src/kubex_manager/
тФВ   тФВ   тФФтФАтФА tests/
тФВ   тФВ
